---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { seoMetadata } from '../lib/constants';

const pageMetadata = seoMetadata['/'];
---

<BaseLayout
  title={pageMetadata.title}
  description={pageMetadata.description}
  ogImage={pageMetadata.ogImage}
>
  <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16 md:py-24">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-[1.3fr_0.7fr] gap-12 items-center">
      <div>
        <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 mb-4">
          Dan Ryan Neff
        </p>

        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-6">
          Good judgment in a changing world.
        </h1>

        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-6">
          I help people make clear, practical decisions about websites, AI, operations, and the digital systems around their work.
        </p>

        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-6">
          Technology works best when it fits the work, the people, and the situation.
        </p>

        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-8">
          Bring me a real situation. Let’s talk.
        </p>

        <div class="flex gap-4 flex-wrap">
          <a
            href="/contact/"
            class="px-8 py-3 bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white font-semibold rounded-lg transition-colors"
          >
            Start a conversation
          </a>

          <a
            href="/work-with-me/"
            class="px-8 py-3 border-2 border-blue-600 text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 dark:border-blue-500 hover:bg-blue-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-800 font-semibold rounded-lg transition-colors"
          >
            Work with me
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex justify-center md:justify-end">
        <img
          src="/images/dan-ryan-neff.webp"
          alt="Portrait of Dan Ryan Neff"
          class="w-64 h-64 md:w-80 md:h-80 object-cover rounded-3xl shadow-lg"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-800 py-16">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-10">
        What people bring to me
      </h2>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-700 p-8 rounded-xl border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 shadow-sm">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">
            A website that no longer fits
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
            Your site may work technically, but no longer reflect the quality, direction, or depth of your work.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-700 p-8 rounded-xl border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 shadow-sm">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">
            Questions about AI
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
            You want to understand where new tools fit, what is worth trying, and what actually makes sense.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-700 p-8 rounded-xl border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 shadow-sm">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">
            Operational friction
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
            Communication, process, tools, or roles feel harder to navigate than they should.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-700 p-8 rounded-xl border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 shadow-sm">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">
            A situation that needs perspective
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
            A decision, idea, opportunity, or challenge feels difficult to think through alone.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">
          Start with a conversation.
        </h2>

        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-6">
          I’m interested in meeting thoughtful people, learning about what they’re working on, and exploring where our interests, challenges, and ideas overlap.
        </p>

        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
          Sometimes that leads to a project. Sometimes it leads somewhere unexpected.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 p-8 rounded-xl border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-700 shadow-sm">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">
          What I build
        </h3>

        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-4">
          I build digital projects that reflect how I think about structure, clarity, creativity, and online experience.
        </p>

        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-6">
          Mandalafy, LandingBio, Systems Atlas, and ImagineThis.Site are part of that portfolio.
        </p>

        <a
          href="/projects/"
          class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 hover:underline font-semibold"
        >
          View projects →
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 pb-16">
    <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-700 rounded-xl p-8 shadow-sm">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">
        Email List
      </h2>

      <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-4 max-w-2xl">
        I occasionally send emails about topics I’m exploring, projects I’m building, and ideas I’m thinking through.
      </p>

      <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-6 max-w-2xl">
        Joining my email list is a step toward a closer connection, and I appreciate your support.
      </p>

      <iframe
        src="https://embeds.beehiiv.com/7b7905fd-bdf1-49b9-9cbc-754021ddf12e?slim=true"
        data-test-id="beehiiv-embed"
        height="52"
        frameborder="0"
        scrolling="no"
        style="width:100%;max-width:520px;margin:0;border-radius:0;background-color:transparent;"
      ></iframe>

      <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 mt-4">
        After subscribing, check your email for a confirmation message.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>